2018 Begins - 2018 has begun. In this New Year’s edition of “World News and the Bible” Steve Wohlberg discusses the End-Times, 2017 sex scandals, current protests in Iran, a recent asteroid that just missed planet Earth, the future, the soon return of Jesus Christ, and His gracious offer of salvation for all.

Program #12 in the World News and the Bible series.
